    BiFunction<Number,​Number,​Number>, BinaryOperator<Number>
    public class Product
extends NumericAggregateFunction
    A Product is a BinaryOperator that takes in Numbers of the same type and calculates the product. If you know the type of number that will be used then this can be set by calling setMode(NumberType), otherwise it will be automatically set for you using the class of the first number passed in.
